---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Research & White Papers">
	<div class="bg-mesh"></div>
	<div class="bg-grid"></div>

	<section class="research-hero container animate-fade-in">
		<div class="hero-layout">
			<div class="hero-left">
				<span class="mono-label">// 003 // THEORY_VAULT</span>
				<h1 class="page-title">ELITE_ <br/><span class="text-outline">RESEARCH</span></h1>
				<p class="page-subtitle">ADVANCING THE BOUNDARIES OF AI_INFRASTRUCTURE THROUGH RIGOROUS INFERENCE OPTIMIZATION, ELITE EXPERIMENTATION, AND PEER-REVIEWED COLLABORATION.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="papers container">
		<div class="papers-grid">
			<article class="paper-card glass-card animate-fade-in">
				<div class="paper-meta">
					<span class="mono-label">TYPE // AI_SECURITY</span>
					<span class="mono-label">DATE // 03.2025</span>
				</div>
				<h3>HUMAN_IN_THE_LOOP_SECURITY</h3>
				<p>AN INVESTIGATION INTO THE RISKS OF AUTOMATED PULL REQUEST APPROVALS AND THE NECESSITY OF ENFORCEABLE SAFETY RAILS.</p>
				<a href="/taq-web/media_vault" class="link">READ_GS_PAPERS &rarr;</a>
			</article>

			<article class="paper-card glass-card animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.1s">
				<div class="paper-meta">
					<span class="mono-label">TYPE // INFRA_OPS</span>
					<span class="mono-label">DATE // 01.2025</span>
				</div>
				<h3>MODULAR_INFRA_STRATEGIES</h3>
				<p>EXPLORING THE SHIFT FROM MONOLITHIC IAC TO MODULAR, COMPOSABLE INFRASTRUCTURE COMPONENTS FOR GLOBAL SCALE.</p>
				<a href="/taq-web/media_vault" class="link">READ_GS_PAPERS &rarr;</a>
			</article>

			<article class="paper-card glass-card animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.2s">
				<div class="paper-meta">
					<span class="mono-label">TYPE // SEC_MANAGEMENT</span>
					<span class="mono-label">DATE // 11.2024</span>
				</div>
				<h3>SLA_DRIVEN_VULN_MGMT</h3>
				<p>A STATISTICAL ANALYSIS OF FIX-TIMES AND THEIR IMPACT ON REDUCING THE ATTACK SURFACE OF MICROSERVICES.</p>
				<a href="/media_vault" class="link">READ_GS_PAPERS &rarr;</a>
			</article>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="research-preview container animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.4s">
		<div class="glass-card preview-card">
			<span class="mono-label">// RESEARCH_OBJECTIVE // STRATEGIC_OVERVIEW</span>
			<div class="video-aspect">
				<iframe 
					width="100%" 
					height="100%" 
					src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/sFr7Uynu8GY" 
					title="RESEARCH_GOAL_DEMO" 
					frameborder="0" 
					allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" 
					allowfullscreen>
				</iframe>
			</div>
			<div class="preview-info">
				<p>A COMPREHENSIVE OVERVIEW OF OUR THEORETICAL FRAMEWORKS AND LONG-TERM SYSTEMIC GOALS.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="collaboration container">
		<article class="glass-card animate-fade-in" style="text-align: center; padding: 8rem 4rem;">
			<span class="mono-label">// 007 // ACADEMIC_OPS</span>
			<h2 style="font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem); margin: 2.5rem 0;">ACADEMIC_PARTNERSHIPS</h2>
			<p style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 5rem;">WE ARE ALWAYS SEEKING RESEARCHERS AND ACADEMIC PARTNERS TO EXPLORE THE NEXT FRONTIER OF SECURE SOFTWARE SYSTEMS.</p>
			<div class="divider" style="max-width: 200px; margin: 0 auto 5rem;"></div>
			<a href="mailto:research@taqlab.com" class="btn btn-primary">PROPOSE_INITIATIVE_OPS</a>
		</article>
	</section>

	<style>
		.research-hero {
			padding: 15rem 0 10rem;
		}

		.page-title {
			font-size: clamp(4rem, 15vw, 10rem);
			margin: 2.5rem 0;
			line-height: 0.85;
			letter-spacing: -0.04em;
		}

		.page-subtitle {
			font-family: var(--font-mono);
			font-size: 0.95rem;
			color: var(--text-muted);
			max-width: 500px;
			letter-spacing: 0.05em;
			line-height: 1.8;
		}

		.papers {
			padding: 6rem 0 15rem;
		}

		.papers-grid {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
			gap: 2rem;
		}

		.paper-meta {
			display: flex;
			justify-content: space-between;
			margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
		}

		.paper-card {
			padding: 4rem;
		}

		.paper-card h3 {
			font-size: 2.2rem;
			margin: 1.5rem 0;
			line-height: 1.1;
			letter-spacing: -0.02em;
		}

		.paper-card p {
			font-family: var(--font-mono);
			font-size: 0.95rem;
			color: var(--text-muted);
			margin-bottom: 4.5rem;
			line-height: 1.8;
		}

		.link {
			font-family: var(--font-mono);
			font-size: 0.85rem;
			font-weight: 700;
			color: var(--accent-primary);
			letter-spacing: 0.15em;
		}

		.collaboration {
			padding-bottom: 15rem;
		}

		.research-preview {
			padding: 0 0 15rem;
		}

		.preview-card {
			padding: 6rem;
		}

		.video-aspect {
			aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
			background: #000;
			margin: 4rem 0;
			border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
		}

		.preview-info p {
			font-family: var(--font-mono);
			font-size: 0.95rem;
			color: var(--text-muted);
			text-align: center;
			letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		}

		@media (max-width: 768px) {
			.page-title {
				font-size: 4.5rem;
			}
			.papers-grid {
				grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			}
		}
	</style>
</Layout>
